)\">abandonment issues</span> ⧽</p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 62, 15)\"><strong>-</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 73, 60)\"><strong>`</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 152, 109)\"><strong>ꨄ︎</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"53852283-d78b-44ac-a50d-126f051daaa4_c0f16c34-ef2b-4282-8f4f-ac3e2ecd0a90.webp","creator":"picavere","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🙇 Submissive","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","👩‍❤️‍👩 WLW","👩 FemPov"],"chats":8917,"messages":267808,"created_at":"2023-11-14T19:13:13.972945+00:00"}